    "description": "利用鸟瞰视角来控制你的单位，你需要将它们适当地安置在最合适的位置，以达到目标。你还可以命令攻击敌人，跟随一个单位，将选定的单位置于防御或进攻模式，并且甚至可以为这些选定的单位设置一个顺序列表，按照其中的点进行访问。你还可以使用地图快速跳转到某个位置，或者指示你的队友前往某个位置执行动作。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/c9481b7e6bd878e2484a9f946e087b95.poster.avif?t=1726273887\" width=480 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/c9481b7e6bd878e2484a9f946e087b95.webm?t=1726273887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/c9481b7e6bd878e2484a9f946e087b95.mp4?t=1726273887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏中有不同类型的单位，它们的移动速度、抗伤能力、武器类型以及特殊能力会有所不同。如果你想更加精确地控制某个特定的单位，你可以操控它们。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/1b42aaaee038d6de81a3cd16070848d9.poster.avif?t=1726273887\" width=480 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/1b42aaaee038d6de81a3cd16070848d9.webm?t=1726273887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/1b42aaaee038d6de81a3cd16070848d9.mp4?t=1726273887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你是一个（头像类型的）角色，学习掌握灵魂出窍的技能，当你的身体自动进入梦游状态时，你将全神贯注于制定一项能带领你的小队取得胜利的战略。<br>头像类型可以是各种类型的单位，例如：<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/9d5f7d7cd18ff6b22c175bf39148614d.poster.avif?t=1726273887\" width=480 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/9d5f7d7cd18ff6b22c175bf39148614d.webm?t=1726273887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/9d5f7d7cd18ff6b22c175bf39148614d.mp4?t=1726273887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你可以预先编辑你的角色，角色编辑器允许你修改性别、身高、年龄、肌肉、体型、皮肤、头发、服装、服装颜色、面部特征和胡须长度等等。所有的游戏角色都具有相同的随机生成特征。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/3995b3d7fc942c66adefb945a774680f.poster.avif?t=1726273887\" width=480 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/3995b3d7fc942c66adefb945a774680f.webm?t=1726273887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257940/extras/3995b3d7fc942c66adefb945a774680f.mp4?t=1726273887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
